    <item>
      <title>中国股市“疯狂”波动引发史上最大交易狂潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/-crazy-chinese-stock-swings-ignite-biggest-ever-trading-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，黄金周假期过后，中国大陆股市重新开市，股票交易员们已经做好了迎接异常繁忙交易的准备。但很少有人为开市时就出现的激烈交易做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/-crazy-chinese-stock-swings-ignite-biggest-ever-trading-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:08:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行改组财富管理部门，扩大超级富豪业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/commerzbank-revamps-wealth-unit-to-grow-business-with-ultra-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 正在加大力度为超级富豪提供财富管理服务，以增加费用收入并抵御竞争对手意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 的主动接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/commerzbank-revamps-wealth-unit-to-grow-business-with-ultra-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Al Rajhi 签署今年中东银行最大笔贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/al-rajhi-inks-largest-middle-east-bank-loan-for-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沙特阿拉伯阿尔拉吉银行（Al Rajhi Bank）已筹集了 19.2 亿美元的可持续发展相关伊斯兰银团贷款，这是今年中东银行最大的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/al-rajhi-inks-largest-middle-east-bank-loan-for-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
